  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\nReconciliation of new notifications into the app db state stopped working after https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/14333 got merged.\r\n\r\n#### Solution\r\n\r\nThe fix is not complicated. We need to take in consideration the difference in semantics between filtering `:all` instead of `:read` and update the private function `status-im.activity-center/update-notifications`.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n- When the user interacts with a notification and its status changes, the UI should immediately reflect the changes.\r\n- When the user is in the Activity Center screen and new notifications arrives, the UI should automatically show them without requiring the user to refresh the screen.",
